      "message": "for (xpath : xpaths) {\n   cpsPathQuery = CpsPathUtil.getCpsPathQuery(xpath)\n   normalizedXPathsToDelete.add(cpsPathQuery.xPath)\n   if (!cpsPathQuery.isPathToListElement() {\n        normalizedXPathsToListElements.add(xPath)\n   }\n}\nfragmentRepository.deleteFragmentsByAnchorIdAndXPath(...)\ndeletePotentialWholeList(...)\n\n\n\n\nprivate deletePotentialWholeList(normalizedXPathsToDelete, normalizedXPathsToListElements) {\n  xPathsToPotentialList = normalizedXPathsToDelete.removeAll(normalizedXPathsToListElements)\n  potentiaListXPathPatterns = xPathsToPotentialList.stream( concat with [%]).collection\n  fragmentRepository.deleteFragmentsByAnchorIdAndXPathPattern(xPathPatterns)\n}",
